#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While most of the functionality offered by &plasma; can be accessed using a "
"simple <quote>point and click</quote> interface, many people prefer using "
"the keyboard for some tasks. Pressing something like <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> is often just faster than moving "
"your hands off the keyboard to the mouse, opening the <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu> menu and selecting <guimenuitem>Find</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Medtem, ko je večina delovanja, ki ga ponuja &plasma; dostopna z uporabo "
"preprostega <quote>pokaži in klikni</quote> vmesnika, veliko ljudi raje "
"uporablja tipkovnico za nekatera opravila. Pritiskanje kot je <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> je pogosto hitreje kot "
"premikanje vaših rok iz tipkovnice na miško, odpiranje menuja "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> in izbiranje <guimenuitem>Najdi</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As different people have different preferences about keyboard shortcuts, "
"&plasma; offers full customization of <quote>key bindings.</quote> A key "
"binding or shortcut is a combination of an action with a key or a "
"combination of keys."
msgstr ""
"Ker različni ljudje imajo različne težnje za bližnjice s tipkovnico, vam "
"&plasma; ponuja popolnoma prosto izbiro za določanje tako imenovanih "
"<quote>tipkovnih vezi</quote>. Tipkovna vez ali bližnjica je kombinacija "
"dejanja s tipko ali kombinacijo tipk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Shortcuts and Global Shortcuts"
msgstr "Standardne bližnjice in globalne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Standard shortcuts and Global shortcuts work just the same. Actually, in a "
"certain way standard or application shortcuts are <quote>global</quote> as "
"well. The only difference is:"
msgstr ""
"Standardne bližnjice in globalne bližnjice delujejo enako. Pravzaprav so "
"standardne bližnjice ali bližnjice aplikacij na nek način tudi "
"<quote>globalne</quote>. Edina razlika je:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Standard shortcuts</quote> refer to actions that are often available "
"in applications, such as Save, Print, Copy &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<quote>Standardne bližnjice</quote> se nanašajo na dejanja, ki so pogosto na "
"voljo v aplikacijah, kot so Shrani, Natisni, Kopiraj &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Global shortcuts</quote> are shortcuts for actions that make sense "
"even when no application is opened. These shortcuts usually refer to actions "
"like switching desktops, manipulating windows &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<quote>Globalne bližnjice</quote> so bližnjice za dejanja, ki so smiselna, "
"tudi če ni odprt noben program. Te bližnjice se običajno nanašajo na "
"dejanja, kot so preklapljanje namizij, upravljanje oken &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note, that the application shortcuts configured here are "
"<emphasis>only</emphasis> the standard actions often found in applications. "
"Most applications will define their own actions as well, for which you have "
"to customize key bindings using the application's key bindings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Vedite, da bližnjice do programov, ki so tukaj nastavljene so "
"<emphasis>samo</emphasis> standardna dejanja, ki se pogosto najdejo v "
"aplikacijah. Veliko aplikacij določa tudi lastna dejanja, za katera morate "
"prilagoditi tipkovne vezi z uporabo pogovornega okna za določanje bližnjic "
"do programov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard Shortcuts page"
msgstr "Stran Standardne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of this dialog you see an input box, where you can search "
"interactively for shortcut names (&eg; Copy) or combination of keys (&eg; "
"<quote><userinput>Ctrl+C</userinput></quote>) by typing them literally here."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu tega pogovornega okna je prikazano vnosno polje, v katerem lahko "
"interaktivno poiščete imena bližnjic (&eg; Kopiraj) ali kombinacije tipk "
"(&eg; <quote><userinput>Ctrl+C</userinput></quote>) tako, da jih tukaj "
"dobesedno vnesete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below the search box you can see a list of key bindings, &ie; associations "
"between actions (&eg; Copy) shown in the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> column "
"and keys or combination of keys (&eg; <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo>) shown in the <guilabel>Shortcut</guilabel> "
"or <guilabel>Alternate</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Pod poljem za iskanje si lahko ogledate seznam vezav tipk, &ie; povezave med "
"akcijami (&eg; Kopiraj), prikazanimi v stolpcu <guilabel>Akcija</guilabel>, "
"in tipkami ali kombinacijo tipk (&eg; <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>C</keycap> </keycombo>), prikazanimi v stolpcu <guilabel>Zkrajšava</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>Alternativa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global Shortcuts page"
msgstr "Stran Globalne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the left of this page is a list box which allows you to select a "
"<guilabel>Component</guilabel> like KWin, Plasma Desktop &etc; The defined "
"shortcuts for the selected component are displayed in the <guilabel>Action</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Global</guilabel> column in the list view."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani je polje s seznamom, v katerem lahko izberete "
"<guilabel>Komponenta</guilabel>, kot so KWin, Plasma Desktop &etc;. "
"Opredeljene bližnjice za izbrano komponento so prikazane v stolpcu "
"<guilabel>Akcija</guilabel> in <guilabel>Global</guilabel> v pogledu seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page has the same search box as the <guilabel>Standard Shortcuts</"
"guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran ima enako iskalno polje kot zavihek <guilabel>Standardne bližnjice</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> or "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> to add or "
"remove a component."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-"
"add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> ali "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"remove.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> za dodajanje "
"ali odstranjevanje komponente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding a component opens a dialog to pick applications from the start menu "
"structure to add launchers to be usable as shortcuts. If an application has "
"jumplist options they will be available as actions."
msgstr ""
"Z dodajanjem komponente se odpre pogovorno okno za izbiro aplikacij iz "
"strukture začetnega menija in dodajanje zaganjalnikov, ki jih je mogoče "
"uporabljati kot bližnjice. Če ima aplikacija možnosti na seznamu skokov, "
"bodo na voljo kot dejanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guilabel>File</guilabel> drop down box at the right to import/"
"export a Scheme, set all shortcuts to none."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uvoziti/izvoziti shemo, kliknite spustno polje <guilabel>Datoteka</"
"guilabel> na desni strani in nastavite vse bližnjice na ne(none)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Global shortcuts can now be configured to jump to specific tasks within an "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Globalne bližnjice je zdaj mogoče konfigurirati za preskok na določena "
"opravila v aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default you can open the application menu by just pressing the &Meta; key."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto lahko meni aplikacije odprete tako, da pritisnete tipko &Meta;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Key Bindings"
msgstr "Nastavitev tipkovnih vezi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configuring key bindings is pretty easy. In the middle of these "
"&systemsettings; modules you will find a list of available actions. If "
"there's a key binding configured for that action you will find it in the "
"columns right to it. Just select the action you want to configure."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija vezav tipk je precej preprosta. V sredini teh modulov "
"&systemsettings; najdete seznam razpoložljivih akcij. Če je za to dejanje "
"konfigurirana vezava ključa, jo boste našli v stolpcih desno od njega. "
"Izberite dejanje, ki ga želite konfigurirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After you have selected an action in the list you will notice that this item "
"is highlighted and you see two additional check boxes below this item in the "
"list view. There you can configure a combination of keys or maybe no key "
"binding at all for the selected action."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete dejanje na seznamu, boste opazili, da je ta element označen in "
"da sta pod tem elementom v pogledu seznama vidna še dva dodatna potrditvena "
"polja. Tam lahko za izbrano dejanje konfigurirate kombinacijo tipk ali morda "
"sploh ne želite vezave tipk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default</guilabel>: the selected action will be associated with "
"&kde;'s default value. This is a good choice for most actions, as &kde; "
"comes with reasonable key bindings we have thought about."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel>: izbrano dejanje bo povezano s privzeto "
"vrednostjo &kde;. To je dobra izbira za večino akcij, saj ima &kde; na voljo "
"razumne vezave tipk, na katere smo se spomnili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel>: if this option is enabled, you can create a key "
"combination for the selected action. Click on the button labeled either "
"<guibutton>None</guibutton> or labeled with the previously selected custom "
"shortcut. Now the button label changes to <guibutton>Input</guibutton>. Then "
"press any modifier key (&ie; &Shift;, &Ctrl;, or &Alt;) and then normal key "
"or a function key (&eg; <keycap>F11</keycap>) you want to assign to this key "
"combination."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Po meri</guilabel>: če je ta možnost omogočena, lahko ustvarite "
"kombinacijo tipk za izbrano dejanje. Kliknite gumb, ki je označen kot "
"<guibutton>Nič</guibutton> ali kot prej izbrana bližnjica po meri. Zdaj se "
"oznaka gumba spremeni v <guibutton>Vnos</guibutton>. Nato pritisnite katero "
"koli modifikacijsko tipko (&ie; &Shift;, &Ctrl; ali &Alt;) in nato običajno "
"tipko ali funkcijsko tipko (&eg; <keycap>F11</keycap>), ki jo želite "
"dodeliti tej kombinaciji tipk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <guilabel>Alternate</guilabel> column of a row in the list "
"allows to edit the second shortcut for the action."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na stolpec <guilabel>Alternirajoče</guilabel> vrstice na seznamu "
"lahko uredite drugo bližnjico za dejanje."

